A cyberpunk-style illustration of a sleek robotic hand with glowing cyan circuitry reaching into a holographic browser window floating in mid-air, manipulating toggle switches and checkboxes inside the interface. The scene is set against a dark cityscape with neon purple and electric blue reflections. Multiple translucent UI panels cascade in layers behind the main window, each containing abstract form elements and sliders. Digital rain particles fall softly in the background. The robotic arm emerges from shadows below, its joints emitting soft amber light. The overall mood is one of precise automation meeting complex web interfaces, with a sense of elegant technical control over chaotic digital systems.
